'''A_EntityAttack'''<br />
(no parameters)

Produces one of five random attacks:
# Same as [[A_SpotLightning]]
# Shoots a {{Class|SpectralLightningH3}}
# Same as [[A_Spectre3Attack]]
# Shoots a {{Class|SpectralLightningBigV2}}
# Shoots a {{Class|SpectralLightningBigBall2}}

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|EntityBoss}} and derived classes.

